source:
TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_SEQ_00<tab>Qhoterl Pasol has the look of someone who hasn't had all she can eat.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
target:
TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var>特殊ルール： レベルアジャスト受注クラス・ジョブ制限<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
※本クエストは受注時のクラスでのみ進行します。

ホパル古盤のコテルリ・パソリは、ソワソワしているようだ。

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_TODO_00<tab>Speak with the poultryman at Slitherbough.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_TODO_00<tab>スリザーバウの養鶏家と話す

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_TODO_01<tab>Use the large sack to capture the clucking chicken.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_TODO_01<tab>スリザーバウの逃げ出したニワトリに<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E902401 /var>を使う

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_TODO_02<tab>Deliver the clucking sack to the poultryman.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_TODO_02<tab>スリザーバウの養鶏家に<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E902501 /var>を渡す

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_TODO_03<tab>Deliver the splendid eggs to Qhoterl Pasol.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_TODO_03<tab>コテルリ・パソリに<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E902601 /var>を渡す

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_QHOTERLPASOL_000_000<tab>The other day residents from Slitherbough brought a gift most divine─chicken eggs! And let me tell you, to say that their flavor was transcendent hardly begins to describe the experience!
target:
TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_QHOTERLPASOL_000_000<tab>先日、スリザーバウの親切なヒトたちから、
ニワトリの卵をお裾分けいただきましたのでございまするが～、
これが、この世のものとは思えぬほど、美味しゅうございまして～！

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_QHOTERLPASOL_000_001<tab>I had scarce tasted the first egg when I knew we must have more. Being the enterprising Qitari that I am, I've arranged to exchange our precious stones for their precious eggs. One of nature's bounties for another─a capital bargain if I do say so myself!
target:
TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_QHOTERLPASOL_000_001<tab>もっと食べたいと、必死の形相で取引を持ちかけましたところ～、
命名石に適した輝石と、交換に応じてくださるとのこと～。
そして、待ちに待った輝石が出土した次第でございまする～！

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_QHOTERLPASOL_000_002<tab>We have already delivered our first cache of stones, but someone must pick up the eggs from Slitherbough. If you would be so kind, I'll ensure that you're handsomely compensated!
target:
TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_QHOTERLPASOL_000_002<tab>輝石はすでに届けておりますゆえ、お使いで心苦しいのですが～、
採れたての卵を、受け取ってきてはもらえませぬか～？
もちろん、報酬はお支払いいたしまする～！

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_POULTRYFARMER03829_000_010<tab>I take it you're here about the eggs, then? I'd love to give them to you, but I'm afraid I've run into a snag. One of my chickens fled the coop, you see, clucking like the sky itself was falling down!
target:
TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_POULTRYFARMER03829_000_010<tab>もしや、キタリ族と取引をした卵の件でしょうか？
すみません……実は今すぐに卵を渡せる状況ではなくて……！
脱走癖のあるニワトリが一羽、逃げ出してしまったのです……！

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_POULTRYFARMER03829_000_011<tab>Gods only know where she is now, but I reckon I'd find her quicker if I had another set of eyes looking for her. What say you? Lend a hand and I'll give you the pick of my best eggs!
target:
TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_POULTRYFARMER03829_000_011<tab>まだ、スリザーバウの中にいるとは思うのですが……！
すみませんが、ご一緒に探していただけないでしょうか！？
もし捕まえてくださいましたら、お礼に多めに卵を渡しますので！

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_POULTRYFARMER03829_000_012<tab>If you catch sight of her, use this sack to scoop her up. I'll stay around the village, while you go ahead and look around the outskirts─I reckon you might hear her before you see her!
target:
TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_POULTRYFARMER03829_000_012<tab>見つけたら、この「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E902401 /var>」を使って捕まえてください！
私は念のため、村の周囲を見てきます！
あなたはスリザーバウの中をお願いしますね！

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_POULTRYFARMER03829_000_020<tab>I've searched everywhere, but I haven't seen hide nor down of that pesky bird. I hope you've had better luck than me.
target:
TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_POULTRYFARMER03829_000_020<tab>村の周囲をひと通り探しましたが、見つかりませんでした……。
あなたの方はいかがでしたか？

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_POULTRYFARMER03829_000_021<tab>Ah, that's her all right! You're a godssend! I was worried she'd been gobbled up whole by some bigger animal. She always lays the best eggs─it would've been a tragedy to lose her.
target:
TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_POULTRYFARMER03829_000_021<tab>いやあ、助かりました……本当にありがとうございます！
森に逃げ込んでいたら、魔物に食べられていたかもしれません！
ニワトリの卵は、私たちにとっても貴重な栄養源なのです。

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_POULTRYFARMER03829_000_022<tab>Speaking of eggs, I believe these are for you. And as I promised, here's a few more on top as your just reward. Give my regards to the Qitari, and let them know I'm open for business any time!
target:
TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_POULTRYFARMER03829_000_022<tab>お騒がせしてしまいましたが、卵を持って行ってください。
約束通り、多めに入れておきました！
キタリ族にも、よろしくお伝えください！

source:
TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_QHOTERLPASOL_000_030<tab>Would that the Qitari could lay eggs. Hmm, perhaps if I...
Oh! You're back! Do you have them!? Do you!?
target:
TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_QHOTERLPASOL_000_030<tab>たまっ、卵……！
卵は持ってきてくださいましたでしょか～！？

source:
TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_QHOTERLPASOL_000_031<tab>Oh, you have saved─
Hmph, I mean, splendid! These eggs are even more pleasing to behold than the last batch, and there are so many of them! I would've sent one of my workers to fetch these, but the sad truth is that no Qitari could be trusted with the task.
target:
TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_QHOTERLPASOL_000_031<tab>おんやぁ！？
いつもより数が多いでございまする～！？
な、なんと、素晴らしきことでございましょ～！！

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_QHOTERLPASOL_000_032<tab>The eggs would have been devoured before they were one yalm from Slitherbough. That you showed enough restraint to deliver them untouched truly speaks to your heroic pedigree!
target:
TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_QHOTERLPASOL_000_032<tab>卵に目がないキタリの者を使いに出せば、
必ずつまみ食いをして、目減りするものですから～！
興奮が収まりませぬ……誠に感謝、感謝でございまする～！
